# GRAPHICS::GET_IS_HIDEF

## Summary
Returns if running in hidef

## Returns
* **BOOL**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
false = Any resolution < 1280x720
true = Any resolution >= 1280x720
